headline: Amrize shares tumble 10% on big guidance miss, disappointing Q2 print
summary: Investing.com -- Amrize AG (NYSE:AMRZ) (SIX:AMRZ) saw its shares slump more than 10% in premarket trading Thursday after it reported weaker-than-expected second-quarter results, and issued an annual outlook that fell meaningfully below consensus.
